<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>[سورة عبس <span class="c2">(٨٠)</span> : الآيات ١٧ الى ٢٤]<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>قُتِلَ الْإِنْسانُ ما أَكْفَرَهُ <span class="c2">(١٧)</span> مِنْ أَيِّ شَيْءٍ خَلَقَهُ <span class="c2">(١٨)</span> مِنْ نُطْفَةٍ خَلَقَهُ فَقَدَّرَهُ <span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ثُمَّ السَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُ <span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ثُمَّ أَماتَهُ فَأَقْبَرَهُ <span class="c2">(٢١)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ثُمَّ إِذا شاءَ أَنْشَرَهُ <span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> كَلاَّ لَمَّا يَقْضِ ما أَمَرَهُ <span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> فَلْيَنْظُرِ الْإِنْسانُ إِلى طَعامِهِ <span class="c2">(٢٤)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١٧-<span class="c5"> قُتِلَ الْإِنْسانُ ما أَكْفَرَهُ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>قُتِلَ الْإِنْسانُ هلاكا للإنسان.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>ما أَكْفَرَهُ مع إحسان الله إليه.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١٨-<span class="c5"> مِنْ أَيِّ شَيْءٍ خَلَقَهُ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">أي:</span> أما يذكر من أي شىء خلقه؟<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١٩-<span class="c5"> مِنْ نُطْفَةٍ خَلَقَهُ فَقَدَّرَهُ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>مِنْ نُطْفَةٍ من ماء.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>خَلَقَهُ بدأ خلقه.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَقَدَّرَهُ أطواره.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٢٠-<span class="c5"> ثُمَّ السَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُ:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>ثُمَّ السَّبِيلَ ثم الطريق إلى الإيمان.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>يَسَّرَهُ له وأعلمه به.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>٢١-<span class="c5"> ثُمَّ أَماتَهُ فَأَقْبَرَهُ:</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَأَقْبَرَهُ فأكرمه بأن يقبر.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>٢٢-<span class="c5"> ثُمَّ إِذا شاءَ أَنْشَرَهُ:</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>أَنْشَرَهُ أحياه بعد الموت.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>٢٣-<span class="c5"> كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقْضِ ما أَمَرَهُ:</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>كَلَّا حقا.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>لَمَّا يَقْضِ ما أَمَرَهُ الله به من الإيمان والطاعة.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>٢٤-<span class="c5"> فَلْيَنْظُرِ الْإِنْسانُ إِلى طَعامِهِ:</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>فَلْيَنْظُرِ فليتأمل.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>إِلى طَعامِهِ شأن طعامه كيف دبرناه ويسرناه.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>